                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Neutron Standard Reference (2015) www-nds.iaea.org"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The experiment was performed in 2017, the anode and",
                "grid signals of the GIC are used, the uncertainties",
                "of the measurement results were big especially for",
                "the 10B(n,t2a) three-body reaction. To obtain better",
                "results, the experimental data are re-analysed using",
                "the anode and cathode signals of the GIC."
              ]
            }
          ],
